snippet.title: Johnny Depps Daughter DEFENDS Amber Heard | The Gossipy
snippet.description:
Johnny Depps Daughter DEFENDS Amber Heard | The Gossipy

Welcome toThe Gossipy. We make interesting videos about Hollywood in English. We give you a closer look in the lives of celebrities like Kanye West, Ed Sheeran, The Rock, Jay Z, Selena Gomez, Kylie Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Rihanna and 100s more.

So the drama between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard has been going on for quite some time now and it was only a question about time before their families and their opinions would be involved in this mess as well.

Recently, Johnny Depp's daughter Lily-Rose Depp has been dragged into the drama and here is her opinion on the entire thing!

#LilyRoseDepp #JohnnyDepp #JohnnyDeppDaughter
